OL,3,CMore time on social media 'linked to
OL,4,Csmoking and vape use among teenagers'
OL,6,FThe team surveyed 8,987 teenagers for
OL,7,Fthe study, which has been published in
OL,8,Fthe journal Nicotine & Tobacco
OL,9,FResearch.
OL,11,FSome 28.9% of those who responded were
OL,12,Fsmokers, while 23.7% vaped. Some 8.2%
OL,13,Fof the teenagers polled used both.
OL,15,FMental health, socio-economic status
OL,16,Fand past smoking behaviours were also
OL,17,Ffactored in.
