OL,3,CMore time on social media 'linked to
OL,4,Csmoking and vape use among teenagers'
OL,6,FLead author Amrit Kaur Purba, said:
OL,7,F"Our findings advocate for the
OL,8,Fregulation of risky content on social
OL,9,Fmedia and tailored guidance for teens
OL,10,Fon social media use so they can
OL,11,Fnavigate the complex social media
OL,12,Fenvironment.
OL,14,F"Educators, health professionals, and
OL,15,Fcare givers must enhance their social
OL,16,Fmedia literacy to prepare teens for
OL,17,Fthe realities of the social media
OL,18,Flandscape.
