OL,6,FIt comes after Prime Minister Rishi
OL,7,FSunak announced plans to bring in laws
OL,8,Fthat will essentially mean youngsters
OL,9,Fborn on or after January 1, 2009 will
OL,10,Fnever legally be able to buy
OL,11,Fcigarettes.
OL,13,FThere will also be new powers to
OL,14,Fregulate the display, contents,
OL,15,Fflavours and packaging of vapes and
OL,16,Fnicotine products.
OL,18,FThe bill was introduced to Commons
OL,19,Flast month.
